				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well, if it wasn't the best place to talk to my brother from Illinois to Florida, I would cancel right now. I talk to my brother online on everquest...great way to have fun, interact and talk at the same time with 1000 miles inbetween us. I mean...it's not that I mind the $3.00 increase a month...God knows I make plenty enough to cover that.  I just think this...why pay more for the same service? I look back on the times I actually have needed GM assistance, and I realize I got sucky service..flat out. Minimum time I'm thinking was an hour? That's ridiculous. All I can say is this...once Star Wars: Galaxies comes out, I'm game. I'll play this until then unless I get a reasonable offer on my account. LOL. I'm just not one to pay more for the same thing I got a a week ago. Why would I? Well, if anyone is interested in PvP, let me know. If right price is paid, I will sell time on my account, as will my brother.<BR>
Vallon Zek<BR>
52 warrior, 50k or so in gear...40 mage..bout naked...35 bard..bout naked...<BR>
Povar<BR>
